alfredsnippet.snippet:
### Required:
- [x] I have performed a self-review of my own code
- [x] My changes generate no console warnings
- [x] My changes do not violate the style guidelines of this project.
- [x] My changes do not introduce any unreadable or hard-to-understand areas without comments.
- [x] Existing tests pass locally with my changes.
- [x] My changes have no hard coded text
 
 ### House keeping: 
<!-- ignore-task-list-start -->
- [x] I have tested my changes locally with both positive and negative scenarios.
- [x] I have added tests that are passing and prove my fix is effective or that my feature works.
- [ ] I have made corresponding additions/changes to the documentation
- [ ] I have tested my changes for accessibility compliance
<!-- ignore-task-list-end -->
alfredsnippet.name: RevXUI PR Checklist
